                    <h1 class="domdom">22</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/851">Av Festival 12: Still Life (2006)</a></h1>

                    <h2>22 Mar 2012, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Still Life is set in Fengjie, 150 miles from the Three Gorges Dam, the hydroelectric project on the Yangtze River that submerged thousands of towns and displaced more than a million people. Shot while Fengjie was being demolished, the film has a powerful documentary impact, as two people travel there separately to look for their missing spouses. </p>

